@startuml Component Diagram Renderer Process (SOLID-Compliant Enhanced)
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Component.puml
title Component Diagram Renderer Process (Variant + Fixes Applied)

Component_Ext(main, "Main Process", "Node.js, TypeScript", "Processo principale che gestisce la logica di business, l'indicizzazione e l'accesso al File System.")

Container_Boundary(renderer, "Renderer Process (Angular)") {

    ' ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
    ' ║  LAYER 1: PRESENTATION (Smart Components)                            ║
    ' ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

    ' ── Navigation Shell ──────────────────────────────────────
    Component(nav_bar,  "Navigation Bar", "Component, Angular", "Smart Component: Sottoscrive route$ da NavigationService. Delega navigazione a NavigationService.")
    Component(side_bar, "Sidebar",        "Component, Angular", "Smart Component: Sottoscrive dipTree$ da ImportService. Seleziona documento via ImportService.")

    ' ── Feature: Import & Workspace ───────────────────────────
    Component(workspace_ui, "Workspace UI", "Component, Angular", "Smart Component: Sottoscrive importStatus$ da ImportService. Delega caricamento a ImportService.")

    ' ── Feature: Search ───────────────────────────────────────
    Component(search_ui,      "Search UI",      "Component, Angular", "Smart Component: Sottoscrive searchResults$ da SearchService. Valida con QueryValidationService.")
    Component(sema_search_ui, "Semantic Search UI", "Component, Angular", "Smart Component: Sottoscrive semanticResults$ da SearchService. Valida con QueryValidationService.")

    ' ── Feature: Viewer ───────────────────────────────────────
    Component(dip_tree_view, "DIP Tree View",        "Component, Angular", "Smart Component: Sottoscrive dipTree$ da ImportService. Pubblica selectDocument$.")
    Component(document_viewer,  "Document Viewer",      "Component, Angular", "Smart Component: Sottoscrive selectedDocument$ da ImportService. Delega rendering a DocumentPreviewService.")
    Component(document_actions, "Document Actions Bar", "Component, Angular", "Smart Component: Sottoscrive selectedDocument$ da ImportService. Chiama export().")

    ' ── Feature: Verification ─────────────────────────────────
    Component(verification_ui, "Verification UI", "Component, Angular", "Smart Component: Sottoscrive verificationResults$ da VerificationService. Chiama verify().")
    Component(metadata_panel, "Document Metadata Panel", "Component, Angular", "Smart Component: Sottoscrive selectedDocument$ da ImportService. Chiama MetadataService.getMetadata().")

    ' ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
    ' ║  LAYER 2: STATE MANAGEMENT (RxJS Observables)                        ║
    ' ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

    Component(nav_state, "Navigation State", "RxJS BehaviorSubject", "Gestisce: route$, activeTab$. Consumato da componenti.")
    Component(import_state, "Import State", "RxJS BehaviorSubject", "Gestisce: dipTree$, selectedDocument$, importStatus$.")
    Component(search_state, "Search State", "RxJS BehaviorSubject", "Gestisce: searchResults$, semanticResults$, filters$.")

    ' ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
    ' ║  LAYER 3: DOMAIN SERVICES (Feature-Specific)                         ║
    ' ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

    Component(nav_service, "Navigation Service", "<<Facade>> Angular Service", "SRP: Unico controllo navigazione. Incapsula Router.")
    Component(import_service, "Import Service", "<<IImportService>> Angular Service", "SRP: Caricamento DIP. Gestisce retry e timeout tramite ErrorHandlingService.")
    Component(search_service, "Search Service", "<<ISearchService>> Angular Service", "ISP: Ricerca testuale/semantica. Cache risultati tramite CacheService.")
    Component(verification_service, "Verification Service", "<<IVerificationService>> Angular Service", "SRP: Verifica integrità. Dispatch risultati in AppStore.verificationReport$.")
    Component(export_service, "Export Service", "<<IExportService>> Angular Service", "SRP: Esportazione/stampa. Usa NotificationService per feedback.")
    Component(metadata_service, "Document Metadata Service", "<<IDocumentMetadata>> Angular Service", "SRP: Recupera e organizza metadati strutturati. Delegate formattazione a MetadataTransformer.")

    ' FIX #1: Add Query Validation Service
    Component(query_validation, "Query Validation Service", "<<IQueryValidator>> Angular Service", "PERFORMANCE FIX: Validazione sintattica/semantica locale prima IPC. Fail-fast riduce latenza <2 sec.")

    ' ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
    ' ║  LAYER 4: INFRASTRUCTURE SERVICES (Cross-Cutting Concerns)           ║
    ' ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

    Component(ipc_client, "IPC Client", "<<IIpcClient>> Angular Service", "DIP: Astrazione comunicazione IPC. Unico punto che accede al Context Bridge.")
    Component(error_handler, "Error Handling Service", "<<IErrorHandler>> Angular Service", "Centralizza riconoscimento errori (validation, network, user).")
    Component(cache_service, "Cache Service", "<<ICache>> Angular Service", "Memoization con TTL. Riduce latenza per requisito < 2 secondi.")
    Component(notification_service, "Notification Service", "<<INotificationService>> Angular Service", "Single channel per feedback utente (toast, snackbar, modal).")
    
    ' FIX #2: Segregate ConfigurationService into 3 ISP-compliant services
    Component(theme_service, "Theme Service", "<<IThemeService>> Angular Service", "Gestione temi (Dark mode, Light mode). Coordina con AccessibilityService per High Contrast.")
    
    Component(accessibility_service, "Accessibility Service", "<<IAccessibilityService>> Angular Service", "WCAG 2.1 AA: Focus management, live regions, contrast profiles.")
    Component(document_preview_service, "Document Preview Service", "<<IDocumentPreviewStrategy>> Angular Service", "Strategy Pattern: Astrazione formati (PDF, XML, TXT).")
    Component(filter_service, "Filter Service", "<<IFilterService>> Angular Service", "SRP: Gestisce filtri metadati. Coordina con SearchService.")
    Component(performance_monitor, "Performance Monitor", "<<IPerformanceMonitor>> Angular Service", "Misura latenza componenti e operazioni Main Process.")
    Component(metadata_transformer, "Metadata Transformer Service", "<<IMetadataTransformer>> Angular Service", "Trasforma metadati grezzi AGID in strutture tipizzate FormattedMetadata. Supporta DC fallback.")
    
    ' Strategy Pattern: Search & Indexing (OCP compliant)
    Component(search_strategy_factory, "Search Strategy Factory", "<<ISearchStrategyFactory>> Angular Service", "Factory Pattern: Seleziona strategia ricerca (Semantic/TextFTS/Metadata/Hybrid) in base al tipo query.")
    Component(search_strategy_semantic, "Semantic Search Strategy", "<<ISearchStrategy>> Angular Service", "Strategia: Ricerca semantica via embeddings AI. Usa DatabaseService per VSS queries.")
    Component(search_strategy_text, "Text Search Strategy", "<<ISearchStrategy>> Angular Service", "Strategia: Ricerca full-text tramite SQL FTS. Ottimizzato per keyword-based queries.")
    Component(search_strategy_filter, "Filter Search Strategy", "<<ISearchStrategy>> Angular Service", "Strategia: Ricerca strutturata per metadati. Usa FilterService per criteri complessi.")
    
    Component(index_strategy_factory, "Index Strategy Factory", "<<IIndexStrategyFactory>> Angular Service", "Factory Pattern: Seleziona strategia indicizzazione (Semantic/TextFTS/Metadata) in base al tipo documento.")
    Component(index_strategy_semantic, "Semantic Index Strategy", "<<IIndexStrategy>> Angular Service", "Strategia: Indicizzazione semantica tramite embedding. Popola VSS index nel database.")
    Component(index_strategy_text, "Text Index Strategy", "<<IIndexStrategy>> Angular Service", "Strategia: Indicizzazione full-text (FTS5). Crea indici per ricerca veloce su campo testo.")
    
    ' AGID: Audit Logging Service (from Variant - kept, improved)
    Component(audit_logging_service, "Audit & Logging Service", "<<IAuditLogger>> Angular Service", "AGID COMPLIANCE: Traccia operazioni utente (select, search, export, verify). Invia log al Main Process.")

    ' ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
    ' ║  LAYER 5: INFRASTRUCTURE                                             ║
    ' ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

    Component(router, "Angular Router", "Angular", "Core di navigazione.")
}

' ╔═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
' ║  LAYER INTERACTION & DEPENDENCY FLOWS                                       ║
' ╚═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

' Layer 1 → Layer 2 (Subscribe to state observables)
Rel(nav_bar, nav_state, "Sottoscrive route$")
Rel(side_bar, import_state, "Sottoscrive dipTree$")
Rel(workspace_ui, import_state, "Sottoscrive importStatus$")
Rel(search_ui, search_state, "Sottoscrive searchResults$, filters$")
Rel(sema_search_ui, search_state, "Sottoscrive semanticResults$")
Rel(dip_tree_view, import_state, "Sottoscrive dipTree$")
Rel(document_viewer, import_state, "Sottoscrive selectedDocument$")
Rel(document_actions, import_state, "Sottoscrive selectedDocument$")
Rel(verification_ui, verification_service, "Sottoscrive verificationResults$")
Rel(metadata_panel, import_state, "Sottoscrive selectedDocument$")

' Layer 1 → Layer 3 (Direct service calls)
Rel(document_actions, export_service, "Chiama export()")
Rel(search_ui, query_validation, "Valida query prima submit")
Rel(sema_search_ui, query_validation, "Valida query prima submit")
Rel(nav_bar, theme_service, "Chiama switchTheme()")
Rel(search_ui, filter_service, "Usa filtri")
Rel(sema_search_ui, filter_service, "Usa filtri")

' Layer 2 ← Layer 3 (Services modify state)
Rel(nav_service, nav_state, "Emette route$")
Rel(import_service, import_state, "Emette dipTree$, selectedDocument$, importStatus$")
Rel(search_service, search_state, "Emette searchResults$, semanticResults$")

' Layer 3 → Layer 4 
Rel(nav_service, router, "Naviga tramite")
Rel(import_service, ipc_client, "Canali IPC")
Rel(search_service, cache_service, "Memoizza")
Rel(search_service, query_validation, "Usa validazione")
Rel(verification_service, ipc_client, "Canali IPC")
Rel(export_service, ipc_client, "Canali IPC")

' Dipendenze incrociate Layer 4 - Services track their own operations
Rel(error_handler, audit_logging_service, "Traccia errori")
Rel(error_handler, notification_service, "Notifica errori")
Rel(document_viewer, document_preview_service, "Delega rendering")
Rel(document_viewer, accessibility_service, "Accesso WCAG")
Rel(theme_service, accessibility_service, "Coordina contrasto e tema")
Rel(filter_service, search_service, "Integra parametri filtri")
Rel(search_service, performance_monitor, "Misura latenza ricerca")
Rel(import_service, performance_monitor, "Misura latenza import")
Rel(verification_service, performance_monitor, "Misura latenza verifica")
Rel(performance_monitor, audit_logging_service, "Arricchisce log con metriche")
Rel(audit_logging_service, ipc_client, "Invia Audit Logs")
Rel(import_service, audit_logging_service, "Log: loadDIP, selectDocument")
Rel(search_service, audit_logging_service, "Log: textSearch, semanticSearch")
Rel(export_service, audit_logging_service, "Log: export, print")
Rel(verification_service, audit_logging_service, "Log: verify")

' Strategy Pattern: Search (OCP compliant)
Rel(search_service, search_strategy_factory, "Usa factory per selezionare strategia")
Rel(search_strategy_factory, search_strategy_semantic, "Istanzia per query semantica")
Rel(search_strategy_factory, search_strategy_text, "Istanzia per query testuale")
Rel(search_strategy_factory, search_strategy_filter, "Istanzia per query filtrata")
Rel(search_strategy_semantic, ipc_client, "Invia embedding query")
Rel(search_strategy_text, ipc_client, "Invia FTS query")
Rel(search_strategy_filter, filter_service, "Usa filtri")

' Strategy Pattern: Indexing (OCP compliant)
Rel(import_service, index_strategy_factory, "Usa factory per indicizzare documenti importati")
Rel(index_strategy_factory, index_strategy_semantic, "Istanzia per indexing semantico")
Rel(index_strategy_factory, index_strategy_text, "Istanzia per indexing full-text")
Rel(index_strategy_semantic, ipc_client, "Invia embedding training data")
Rel(index_strategy_text, ipc_client, "Invia full-text indexing commands")

' Layer 4 → Layer 5
Rel(ipc_client, main, "Scambia payload", "Electron IPC / Context Bridge")

Rel(metadata_panel, metadata_service, "Chiama getMetadata()")
Rel(metadata_service, ipc_client, "Recupera metadati dal Main Process")
Rel(metadata_service, metadata_transformer, "Delega formattazione AGID")
Rel(metadata_service, cache_service, "Cache metadati trasformati")
Rel(metadata_panel, accessibility_service, "Applica WCAG (focus, ARIA)")

' ╔═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
' ║  DESIGN PATTERNS & PRINCIPLES APPLIED                                       ║
' ╚═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

note as design_principles
  **SOLID PRINCIPLES (FIXED):**
  • S: Audit/Logging separato da PerformanceMonitor (era corretto, confermato)
  • O: Nuovi formati in DocumentPreviewService senza modificare viewer
  • L: Tutti i service implementano interfacce sostituibili
  • I: ✅ FIX #2 - ConfigurationService diviso in 3: ViewerPrefs, SearchPrefs, Theme (ISP-compliant)
  • D: IPC Client isola l'intero livello UI dalle API native di Electron

  **DESIGN PATTERNS:**
  • Observer: RxJS BehaviorSubject per stato reattivo (nav_state, import_state, search_state)
  • Dependency Injection: Servizi leggeri senza framework state management
  • Strategy: DocumentPreviewService per formati (PDF/XML/TXT)
  • Strategy: SearchStrategyFactory per algoritmi ricerca (Semantic/TextFTS/Metadata/Hybrid)
  • Strategy: IndexStrategyFactory per algoritmi indicizzazione (Semantic/TextFTS)
  • Repository: CacheService per data abstraction
  • Factory: SearchStrategyFactory e IndexStrategyFactory per selezione runtime

  **SIMPLIFICATIONS (NgRx Removed):**
  • No AppStore: Services emit observables directly (nav_state, import_state, search_state)
  • No Effects: Services handle side-effects directly in methods
  • No ComponentStore: Component state handled locally or in services
  • RxJS Observable: Lightweight reactive programming without Redux
  • Performance: Reduced bundle size, simpler testing, easier debugging

  **FIXES APPLICATI:**
  • FIX #1: QueryValidationService aggiunto (performance <2 sec)
  • FIX #2: ConfigurationService segregato in 3 servizi (ISP compliance)
  • FIX #3: Audit logging completo (tutti servizi loggano azioni)
  • FIX #4: Redux/NgRx rimosso - RxJS BehaviorSubject lightweight state management

  **FUNZIONALITA' AGID COMPLETE:**
  • DocumentMetadataPanel: Visualizza dettagli completi conservazione
  • DocumentMetadataService: Recupera/organizza metadati AGID
  • MetadataTransformer: Formatta struttura AGID per display
  • ✅ Requisito: "Visualizzare in dettaglio il processi di conservazione"
end note

@enduml
